WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.300 --> 00:00:01.066
Wow

2
00:00:01.066 --> 00:00:04.066
You, it was mom's fault before you heard mom say it

3
00:00:04.133 --> 00:00:05.600
I am blind to Tarzan

4
00:00:05.600 --> 00:00:06.500
I have no eyes

5
00:00:06.500 --> 00:00:07.400
It's all my fault

6
00:00:07.400 --> 00:00:08.600
Can you forgive me?

7
00:00:08.600 --> 00:00:09.400
No, no.

8
00:00:09.400 --> 00:00:12.566
Mom swears that you will love you well in the future

9
00:00:12.566 --> 00:00:13.466
Hurt you well

10
00:00:13.466 --> 00:00:15.600
Can you forgive me?

11
00:00:17.400 --> 00:00:18.700
I am a waste

12
00:00:18.700 --> 00:00:20.100
A loss

13
00:00:20.100 --> 00:00:21.966
A shameless bastard

14
00:00:22.200 --> 00:00:24.866
I don't deserve your mother's love

15
00:00:25.200 --> 00:00:26.000
No.

16
00:00:26.800 --> 00:00:29.766
It was me before that, I was talking nonsense

17
00:00:29.766 --> 00:00:31.400
If you get angry, you hit me.

18
00:00:31.400 --> 00:00:32.900
You hit me! You hit me!

19
00:00:32.933 --> 00:00:34.300
Forgive me, okay?

20
00:00:34.300 --> 00:00:36.366
I can't live without you

21
00:00:37.000 --> 00:00:38.066
You can't live without me

22
00:00:38.066 --> 00:00:40.800
You still can't live without money, you know it yourself

23
00:00:42.066 --> 00:00:45.000
Uh-huh.

24
00:00:45.600 --> 00:00:47.966
I lived half my life

25
00:00:47.966 --> 00:00:49.233
Had a daughter.

26
00:00:50.800 --> 00:00:54.133
When I grew up, he didn't recognize me as a mother anymore

27
00:00:54.133 --> 00:00:57.000
He is a senior now and he doesn't want me anymore.

28
00:00:57.000 --> 00:00:59.000
You are such a white-eyed wolf.

29
00:00:59.100 --> 00:01:00.533
An unfilial daughter like you

30
00:01:00.533 --> 00:01:02.566
How do you represent your country?

31
00:01:04.100 --> 00:01:06.900
Didn't you ask me to kneel down for you before you forgave me?

32
00:01:06.900 --> 00:01:09.000
Ouch, I'm asking

33
00:01:09.333 --> 00:01:12.133
No matter what, he's your mother

34
00:01:12.133 --> 00:01:14.066
You can't do this to him.

35
00:01:14.533 --> 00:01:16.966
One must have a conscience

36
00:01:17.100 --> 00:01:19.500
This daughter makes mom kneel

37
00:01:19.500 --> 00:01:22.000
That's going to be hit by lightning

